<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الباب الثاني والثلاثون والمائة فيما قيل فِي الإِثم<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(١١٦٢)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ زُهِيرُ بْنُ أَبِي سُلْمَى:</span> <span class="c2">(المنسرح)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١ - والإِثْمُ مِنْ شرِّ مَا يُصالُ بِه ... وَالبرُّ كَالْغَيثِ نَبْتُه أَمِرْ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(١١٦٣)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ كَعْبُ بْنُ مَالِكٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(البسيط)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - أنْفِقْ وَأَخْلِفْ وَلا تَكْسَبْ بِمأْثَمَةٍ ... مَالًا وَلا تَكْتَسِبْ مَالاً بِقُنْيَانِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(١١٦٤)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيضًا:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١ - وَلا تَأْكُلُوا مَالاً بإِثْمٍ وَلا يَكُنْ ... مُعَانَدَةً بِالتُرَّهَاتِ وَبِالْغَضَبْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(١١٦٥)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عَبْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ جَعْفَرٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(المتقارب)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١ - أرَى الْمَالَ بِالإثْمِ مِنْ شَرِّ مَا ... يُقَدِّمُهُ الْمَرْءُ قَدَامَهُ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>